.libPathDefault         SpaDES.project default .libPaths() directory
.teardownProject        Helpers for cleanup of global state in examples
                        and tests
SpaDES.project-package
                        Project templates using 'SpaDES'
findProjectPath         Find the project root directory
getGithubFile           A simple way to get a Github file,
                        authenticated
getModule               Simple function to download a SpaDES module as
                        GitHub repository
listModules             Tools for examining modules on known
                        repositories
makeDESCRIPTIONproject
                        Make DESCRIPTION file(s) from SpaDES module
                        metadata
packagesInModules       Extract element from SpaDES module metadata
pkgload2                An alternative to 'pkgload::load_all' with
                        caching
setProjPkgDir           Set the package directory for a project
setupPaths              Individual setup* functions that are contained
                        within 'setupProject'
setupProject            Sets up a new or existing SpaDES project
spadesProjectOptions    'SpaDES.project' options
user                    Helpers to develop easier to understand code.
